      "message": "[Major] Line 177: `setNetworkSimulator()` exposes a production `SocketPair` hook without any build guard even though the simulator is test-only infrastructure. This adds mutable packet-dropping behavior to release builds and broadens the runtime surface unnecessarily. Gate the simulator integration behind a test/build option or keep it in test-only code paths.\\n```suggestion\\n#ifdef ENABLE_NETWORK_SIMULATOR\\n    void setNetworkSimulator(std::shared_ptr\u003cNetworkSimulator\u003e sim)\\n    {\\n        std::lock_guard lock(netSimMutex_);\\n        networkSim_ \u003d std::move(sim);\\n    }\\n#endif\\n```",
